Summary of Key Benefits:


Caching: Automatically caches data to avoid redundant API requests.

Background Synchronization: Keeps data fresh without user intervention.

Optimistic Updates: Instantly reflects UI changes before receiving the server response.

Pagination/Infinite Scrolling: Handles large datasets efficiently.

Offline Support: Ensures the app works even when offline.

Simplified Server-State Management: Manages server-side data without complex state management tools.

Developer-Friendly: Easy-to-use API with React hooks.